The simplest communication app.!!

Server-Client Messaging application.
Base code to setup the sockets was borrowed from :
https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/socket-programming-cc/


c2.cpp > Client Side
  - Compile as  : $ g++ -o c2 c2.cpp
  - Run as      : $ ./c2

s2.cpp > Server Side
  - Compile as  : $ g++ -o s2 s2.cpp
  - Run as      : $ ./s2  
